SAFE TRAVERSAL/NAVIGATION OPERATOR

        task = {
            title: 'Complete Angular Course',
            assigne: null
            completed: false
        }

        <span>{{task.assigne.name}}</span>

        -> error: Object is possibly 'null'

- we can solve this in 2 ways: 
    1) using *ngIf
    2) using safe traversal OPERATOR

2) <span>{{task.assigne?.name}}</span>
    -> if assigne is non-existent or null, the ? won't cause our code to drown in errors.